criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy patient (self-report);

          -  Male gender;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of cancer;

          -  Smokers or alcoholics;

          -  Use drugs that influenced cardiac autonomic activity;

          -  Cardiovascular, metabolic or endocrine diseases;

          -  Occurrence of musculoskeletal injury during the study.
